		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding:0 24px 0 24px;">As we promised last week, we have now upgraded your Study Skills Success to the latest version.</p>
        <p style="margin: 0px 0px 0.5em; padding:0 24px 10px 24px;">For full details, please see <a href="http://www.clarityenglish.com/program/studyskills.php?me=SSSV9_email">www.ClarityEnglish.com/StudySkillsSuccess</a>.</p>
